snippet.title: Pokémon Bronze OUT NOW! - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Download here: http://pokemonbronze.net/ !

After almost two years of work I finally created a new Pokémon game set in the Gen II era with an all new region, trainers to fight, badges to get, and a few new Pokemon.
